###
To move an existing docker data folder, do the following:
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/59345566/move-docker-volume-to-different-partition

1) Stop the docker daemon:

service docker stop

2) Create/Edit the /etc/docker/daemon.json configuration file with location of the new data directory:

{
    "data-root": "/new/path"
}

3) Copy docker files to new location:

rsync -aP /var/lib/docker/ /new/path

4) Remove old directory (rename it to be safe)

mv /var/lib/docker /var/lib/docker.old


